A mathematical solver designed to find the Optimal Vertex in multi-dimensional space. This tool maximizes an objective function (such as profit) while respecting resource constraints (such as machine hours or staff availability).
Technical Logic
Matrix Pivoting: Implemented using NumPy for high-speed Gauss-Jordan elimination.
Slack Variables: Transformation of inequalities into equalities for matrix processing.
Application: Used to calculate the ROI for industrial service operations in Lugbe, Abuja.
